Once we can combine painters, we would like to be able to abstract typical patterns of combining painters. We will implement the painter operations as Scheme procedures JavaScript functions. This means that we dont need a special abstraction mechanism in the picture language: Since the means of combination are ordinary Scheme procedures JavaScript functions, we automatically have the capability to do anything with painter operations that we can do with proceduresfunctions. For example, we can abstract the pattern in wave4wave4 as
flipped_pairs wave4_2
